title: [Grawood Farmstead, Maze]
description: Large stacks of hay dominate the landscape as far as the eye can see.  Well, save for where it is possible to see stalks of corn.  The grayish-yellow hay is bound tightly together in thick, heavy bales and smells of a variety of sweet grasses that have slowly baked in the sun.
room.location: Grawood Farmstead outside of River's Rest
